FortyTwo BBS @VERSION@ for x86_64 Linux
Currently targets glibc-based Linux systems
and is being tested on Ubuntu. Debian support
is planned for the first container deployment.
BSD support is planned for later platform tests.
A complete open-source Bulletin Board System
with Fidonet mailer, tosser, TIC processing,
message areas, doors and file utilities.
Users can connect through Telnet or SSH.
File areas can be published through generated
HTML indexes with downloads and image previews.
Based on MBSE BBS and released under GPLv2.
Project: https://www.ihlau.net
Support: neo67@linuxmintusers.de
